('7b7184d7-f21c-5598-85de-cdf91258219a', '8e57d228-2375-4684-9b15-7e73584141b6', 'She ___ many books from the library yesterday.', '她昨天從圖書館借了一些書。', 'got', 'made', 'took', 'danced', '表示「得到」或「拿到」的意思。', 'Get it! (拿到它)'),
('04c95bdc-796e-50f6-a4c2-c10c3f409c76', 'f64aab4c-6665-4617-a07e-5f6b210dc975', 'I am sorry, I did not quite ___ what you just said.', '很抱歉，我不太明白你剛才說了什麼。', 'get', 'tell', 'feel', 'want', 'get 在口語中有「理解」或「明白」的意思。', 'I get it! → 我懂了！'),
('8766a75a-cc7b-5a8f-bdb5-b8e5331b12d6', '74449081-948e-4337-b24b-e50b8a25cddf', '___ color is your backpack?', '你的書包是什麼顏色的？', 'what', 'which', 'some', 'many', '這是一個疑問形容詞，用來修飾後面的名詞。', '看到問句想問『什麼』，就找 what！'),
('9789b269-55c1-598b-8c5e-4b2562c68d52', '4cb49395-91b8-403d-bb41-77e22ac4ae2f', 'She has a strong ___ to win the game.', '她有強烈的意志要贏得比賽。', 'will', 'dream', 'hope', 'wish', 'will 為單字，無詞根或詞綴。', 'will → 內心的強大意志。');
